stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idling : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> HomingShoulderAndExtension : wanted = HOME
    [*] --> MovingToPosition : wanted = MOVE_TO_POSITION

    HomingShoulderAndExtension --> HomingShoulderAndExtension : velocity above threshold
    HomingShoulderAndExtension --> HomingWrist : velocity below threshold for time period
    HomingWrist --> HomingWrist : wrist velocity above threshold
    HomingWrist --> Idling : wrist velocity below threshold for time period

    note right of HomingShoulderAndExtension
        Drives extension and shoulder
        into hard stop at duty cycle
    end note

    note right of HomingWrist
        Drives wrist into hard stop
        after shoulder/extension tared
    end note

    note right of MovingToPosition
        Sequences shoulder before extension
        when retracting from L4.
        Limits wrist angle based on extension.
    end note
